Enclosing class:
SummaryMetadata
public static final class SummaryMetadata.Builder extends GeneratedMessageV3.Builder<SummaryMetadata.Builder> implements SummaryMetadataOrBuilder
A SummaryMetadata encapsulates information on which plugins are able to make
use of a certain summary value.
Protobuf type tensorflow.SummaryMetadata
